<P>
OCCIDENTAL HIRES SWIM, WATER POLO COACHES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Occidental College has hired coaches for its swimming and water polo teams. 
</P>
<P>
Peggy Lynn Carl, who will coach the men's and women's swimming teams, comes to 
Occidental from Carleton College in Northfield, Minn., where she coached the 
women's team. 
</P>
<P>
After coaching the Glendale High swimming and water polo teams, Pete Loporchio 
will take over the Occidental water polo team. Loporchio majored in physical 
education at Cal State Northridge. 
</P>
