Athletic Club, will begin Saturday at 7:30 a.m. on Fiesta Island. 
</P>
<P>
Competition will continue through Sunday and resume on Saturday and Sunday, 
July 21 and 22. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
BASKETBALL 
</P>
<P>
The third Seagram's Coolers All-Star Basketball game will be played Tuesday, 
Aug. 14, at 7:30 p.m. at the San Diego Sports Arena. 
</P>
