<P>
July 13, 1990, Friday, South Bay Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
LONNIE SUMMERS 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 2 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
